import React from 'react'
import { SidebarContainer, Icon, CloseIcon, SidebarWrapper, SidebarMenu, SidebarLink, SideBtnWrap, SidebarRoute } from './SidebarElements'

const SideBar = ({ isOpenSideBar, toggleSideBar, toggleSignPanel }) => {
  return (
    <SidebarContainer isOpenSideBar={isOpenSideBar}>
        <SidebarMenu>
          <SidebarLink to="/about" onClick={toggleSideBar}>聽聽音樂</SidebarLink>
          <SidebarLink to="/discover" onClick={toggleSideBar}>聊聊音樂</SidebarLink>
          <SidebarLink to="/services" onClick={toggleSideBar}>上傳音樂</SidebarLink>
          <SidebarLink to="/signup" onClick={toggleSideBar}>上傳文章</SidebarLink>
          <SidebarLink to="/signup" onClick={toggleSideBar}>收藏列表</SidebarLink>
          <SidebarLink to="/signup" onClick={toggleSideBar}>會員資料</SidebarLink>
        </SidebarMenu>
        <SideBtnWrap>
          <SidebarRoute onClick={() => {toggleSideBar(); toggleSignPanel()}}>註冊 / 登入</SidebarRoute>
        </SideBtnWrap>
    </SidebarContainer>
  )
}

export default SideBar;
